---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Car Rental DWTC Dubai 2026 — Trade Centre Pickup From AED 35/day"
  description="Compare car rentals near Dubai World Trade Centre. Exhibition visitor rates. Economy from AED 35/day with delivery to DWTC area."
>
<div class="bg-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 mb-2">📍 DWTC / Dubai Trade Centre</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Car Rental DWTC — From AED 35/day</h1>
  <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare car rental companies near Dubai World Trade Centre. Perfect for exhibition visitors and business travellers.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=dwtc" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Get DWTC Car Rental Quotes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-4 mb-10">
    <iframe src="https://www.discovercars.com/engine/rent-a-car/iframe?a_aid=YOUR_AFFILIATE_ID&location=Dubai+World+Trade+Centre&lang=en&curr=AED" width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="DWTC Car Rental — Compare Prices"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Car Rental Near Dubai World Trade Centre</h2>
    <p>Dubai World Trade Centre (DWTC) hosts over 500 exhibitions and events annually, including GITEX, World Art Dubai (April 23–26), and Arabian Travel Market. Visitors typically need a car for 3–5 days during exhibition attendance.</p>
    <p>The DWTC area is centrally located on Sheikh Zayed Road with easy access to Downtown, DIFC, and Business Bay. Car rental companies deliver to nearby hotels including the Novotel, ibis, and Crowne Plaza Trade Centre.</p>
    <p>During major exhibitions, hotel parking can fill up quickly. Booking your rental car before arriving ensures you have transportation lined up. Economy cars from AED 35/day with unlimited mileage within Dubai.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/car-rentals" class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all car rental areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
